### Get All Templates (with filters)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates?page=1&limit=6&search=customer&type=SCREENING&domain=CUSTOMER_SUPPORT_AND_SALES
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Templates (default)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Single Template
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Template
POST http://localhost:3001/api/templates
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Customer Support Representative",
  "description": "This interview template evaluates candidates for customer support roles",
  "domain": "CUSTOMER_SUPPORT_AND_SALES",
  "jobTitle": "Customer Support Representative",
  "jobDescription": "Overview: The Customer Support Representative will handle customer inquiries and provide excellent service.",
  "type": "SCREENING",
  "tags": ["customer-service", "support"],
  "assessments": [
    {
      "assessmentId": "ASSESSMENT_ID_1",
      "weightage": 40,
      "order": 1
    },
    {
      "assessmentId": "ASSESSMENT_ID_2",
      "weightage": 40,
      "order": 2
    },
    {
      "assessmentId": "ASSESSMENT_ID_3",
      "weightage": 20,
      "order": 3
    }
  ]
}

### Update Template
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Customer Support Representative",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "isPublic": true
}

### Clone Template
POST http://localhost:3001/api/templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE/clone
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Delete Template
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/templates/TEMPLATE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Filter by Tags
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates?tags=customer-service&tags=support
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Filter by Created By
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates?createdBy=all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Sort by Duration
GET http://localhost:3001/api/templates?sortBy=duration
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

